 with it. Question put and agreed to. Resolved, That this House has considered the timetable for building Type 26 frigates on the Clyde.     Share           5.28 pm          Sitting adjourned.                     ×   Suggest Correction            Your Details:         Enter your suggested correction:   0 /1000          Please prove you are not a robot.        Close  Submit               A-Z index | Glossary | Contact us | Freedom of Information | Data Protection |  Jobs | Using this website |  Copyright     © Parliamentary Copyright                     Cookies: We use cookies to give you the best possible experience on our site. By continuing to use the site you
